    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor Description
      C_Chronogram​(java.lang.String csvChronoName)
      Retrieve data from a chronogram, put the events of dataChrono array field to allow a direct access and to close the buffer
      The internal chronogram date is in format : dd/mm/yyyy.
      Chronogram format : DATE_COL, X_COL, Y_COL, VALUE1_COL, VALUE2_COL ...
      CSV semicolon separator (;) The csv chronogram file must be in data_csv directory/
